Class IcebergArrowColumnVector

All Implemented Interfaces:
AutoCloseable
Direct Known Subclasses:
ColumnVectorWithFilter
public class IcebergArrowColumnVector extends org.apache.spark.sql.vectorized.ColumnVector
Implementation of Spark's ColumnVector interface. The code for this class is heavily inspired from Spark's ArrowColumnVector The main difference is in how nullability checks are made in this class by relying on NullabilityHolder instead of the validity vector in the Arrow vector.
